{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1040,"text":"I believe big institutions"},{"time":3080,"text":"have unique potential to create change,"},{"time":5720,"text":"and I believe that we as individuals"},{"time":7720,"text":"have unique power"},{"time":9040,"text":"to influence the direction\nthat those institutions take."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12720,"text":"Now, these beliefs did not\ncome naturally to me,"},{"time":15080,"text":"because trusting big institutions,"},{"time":17680,"text":"not really part of my family legacy."},{"time":20640,"text":"My mother escaped North Korea"},{"time":22760,"text":"when she was 10 years old."},{"time":24640,"text":"To do so, she had to elude\nevery big institution in her life:"},{"time":28680,"text":"repressive governments, occupying armies"},{"time":31560,"text":"and even armed border patrols."},{"time":34720,"text":"Later, when she decided she wanted\nto emigrate to the United States,"},{"time":38440,"text":"she had to defy an entire culture"},{"time":40520,"text":"that said the girls would never\nbe the best and brightest."},{"time":44680,"text":"Only because her name\nhappens to sound like a boy's"},{"time":47640,"text":"was she able to finagle her way\ninto the government immigration exam"},{"time":50920,"text":"to come to the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53600,"text":"Because of her bravery and passion,"},{"time":56000,"text":"I've had all the opportunities\nthat she never did,"},{"time":58880,"text":"and that has made my story so different."},{"time":62080,"text":"Instead of running away\nfrom big institutions,"},{"time":64480,"text":"I've actually run toward them."},{"time":66320,"text":"I've had the chance\nover the course of my career"},{"time":68600,"text":"to work for The Wall Street Journal,"},{"time":70440,"text":"the White House"},{"time":71680,"text":"and now one of the largest\nfinancial institutions in the world,"},{"time":74680,"text":"where I lead sustainable investing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76840,"text":"Now, these institutions are like tankers,"},{"time":79280,"text":"and working inside of them,"},{"time":80720,"text":"I've come to appreciate\nwhat large wakes they can leave,"},{"time":84360,"text":"and I've become convinced"},{"time":85680,"text":"that the institution\nof the global capital markets,"},{"time":88440,"text":"the nearly 290 trillion dollars\nof stocks and bonds in the world,"},{"time":93360,"text":"that that may be one\nof our most powerful forces"},{"time":96240,"text":"for positive social change\nat our disposal,"},{"time":98840,"text":"if we ask it to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100920,"text":"Now, I know some of you are thinking,"},{"time":102800,"text":"global capital markets,\npositive social change,"},{"time":105320,"text":"not usually in the same sentence\nor even the same paragraph."},{"time":109160,"text":"I think many people think\nof the capital markets"},{"time":111520,"text":"kind of like an ocean."},{"time":112840,"text":"It's a vast, impersonal,\nuncaring force of nature"},{"time":116680,"text":"that is not affected\nby our wishes or desires."},{"time":119360,"text":"So the best that our\nlittle savings accounts"},{"time":121720,"text":"or retirement accounts can do"},{"time":123440,"text":"is to try to catch some waves\nin the good cycles"},{"time":126040,"text":"and hope that we don't get\ninundated in the turbulent ones,"},{"time":128826,"text":"but certainly our decisions on how\nto steer our little retirement accounts"},{"time":133080,"text":"don't affect the tides,"},{"time":134600,"text":"don't change the shape or size\nor direction of the waves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139800,"text":"But why is that?"},{"time":141040,"text":"Because actually,\none third of this ocean of capital"},{"time":144400,"text":"actually belongs to individuals like us,"},{"time":148040,"text":"and most of the rest\nof the capital markets"},{"time":150120,"text":"is controlled by the institutions\nthat get their power and authority"},{"time":153360,"text":"and their capital from us,"},{"time":155160,"text":"as members, participants,\nbeneficiaries, shareholders or citizens."},{"time":159320,"text":"So if we are the ultimate owners\nof the capital markets,"},{"time":163240,"text":"why aren't we able\nto make our voices heard?"},{"time":166360,"text":"Why can't we make some waves?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168960,"text":"So let me ask you a different question:"},{"time":170880,"text":"did any of you buy fair trade coffee"},{"time":173120,"text":"the last time you were\nat a supermarket or at Starbucks?"},{"time":175800,"text":"OK. Do any of you go to the restaurant"},{"time":178240,"text":"and order the sustainably farmed trout"},{"time":180920,"text":"instead of the miso-glazed\nChilean sea bass"},{"time":183480,"text":"that you really wish you could have?"},{"time":185960,"text":"Do any of you drive hybrid cars\nor even electric cars?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":189440,"text":"So why do we do these things?"},{"time":191560,"text":"Right? One electric car doesn't amount\nto much in a fleet of 1.2 billion"},{"time":195440,"text":"combustion engine vehicles."},{"time":197760,"text":"One fish is just one fish in the sea."},{"time":201160,"text":"And one cup of coffee"},{"time":203360,"text":"doesn't amount to a hill of beans\nin this crazy world."},{"time":207400,"text":"But we do these things\nbecause we believe they matter,"},{"time":209960,"text":"that our actions add up,"},{"time":211240,"text":"that our choices might influence others"},{"time":213160,"text":"and collectively,\nwhat an impact we can have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216440,"text":"So, in my bag I have a coffee mug\nthat I bought a couple of years ago."},{"time":219880,"text":"It's a reusable mug.\nIt has all these things printed on it."},{"time":222840,"text":"Look at some of the things\nthat are on it, that it says."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225960,"text":"\"This one cup can be used\nagain and again.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":228520,"text":"\"This one cup may inspire others\nto use one too.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":232400,"text":"\"This one cup helps save the planet.\""},{"time":234720,"text":"I had no idea this plastic cup\nwas so powerful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":238320,"text":"So why do we think that our choice"},{"time":240240,"text":"of a four dollar shade-grown\nfair trade artisanal cup of coffee"},{"time":244080,"text":"in a reusable mug matters,"},{"time":246280,"text":"but what we do with 4,000 dollars\nin our investment account"},{"time":249066,"text":"for our IRA doesn't?"},{"time":251800,"text":"Why can't we tell the supermarket\nand the capital markets"},{"time":254920,"text":"that we care,"},{"time":256360,"text":"that we care about fair labor standards,"},{"time":258640,"text":"that we care about sustainable\nproduction methods"},{"time":261000,"text":"and about healthy communities?"},{"time":262880,"text":"Why aren't we voting\nwith our investment dollars,"},{"time":265920,"text":"but we would vote with our lattes?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":268520,"text":"So I think it has something\nto do with the myths,"},{"time":271760,"text":"the fables that we all carry around\nin our collective consciousness."},{"time":275000,"text":"Do you remember the Grimm's fairy tale\nabout the magic porridge pot?"},{"time":278600,"text":"If you said to the pot,\n\"Boil, little pot, boil,\""},{"time":281000,"text":"it would fill up with sweet porridge."},{"time":283320,"text":"And if you said, \"Stop, little pot, stop,\""},{"time":285440,"text":"it would stop."},{"time":287440,"text":"But if you got the words wrong,\nit wouldn't listen,"},{"time":290640,"text":"and things could go terribly awry."},{"time":293640,"text":"So I think when it comes to markets,"},{"time":295400,"text":"we have a little bit\nof a similar fable in our heads."},{"time":297920,"text":"We believe that the markets\nis this magic pot"},{"time":300280,"text":"that obeys only one command:"},{"time":302160,"text":"make more money."},{"time":304920,"text":"Only those words said exactly that way"},{"time":307840,"text":"will make the pot fill up with gold."},{"time":310640,"text":"Add in some extra words\nlike \"protect the environment,\""},{"time":314000,"text":"the spell might not work."},{"time":316400,"text":"Put in the wrong words\nlike \"promote social justice,\""},{"time":320560,"text":"and you might see your gold coins shrink"},{"time":322600,"text":"or even vanish entirely,\naccording to this fable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326440,"text":"So we asked people,\nwhat do you really think?"},{"time":329240,"text":"And we actually went out and polled\na thousand individual investors,"},{"time":333480,"text":"and we found something fascinating."},{"time":335520,"text":"Overwhelmingly,"},{"time":337040,"text":"people wanted to add\nthose extra words into the formula."},{"time":340680,"text":"71 percent of people said yes,"},{"time":343760,"text":"they were interested\nin sustainable investing,"},{"time":346360,"text":"which we define as taking the best\nin class investment process"},{"time":349320,"text":"that you already have traditionally"},{"time":351080,"text":"and adding in the extra\ninformation you get"},{"time":353160,"text":"when you think about the environment\nand society and good governance."},{"time":356440,"text":"71 percent wanted that."},{"time":358200,"text":"72 percent said that they believe\nthat companies who did that"},{"time":361880,"text":"would actually do better financially."},{"time":363720,"text":"So people really do believe\nthat you can do well by doing good."},{"time":367400,"text":"But here was the weird thing:"},{"time":368840,"text":"54 percent of the people"},{"time":370400,"text":"still said if they put their money\nin those kinds of stocks,"},{"time":374600,"text":"they thought that they\nwould make less money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377880,"text":"So is it true?"},{"time":379520,"text":"Do you get less sweet porridge\nif you invest in shade-grown coffee"},{"time":383320,"text":"instead of drinking it?"},{"time":385840,"text":"Well, you know, the investors\nin companies like Burt's Bees"},{"time":389040,"text":"or Ben &amp; Jerry's wouldn't say so."},{"time":390840,"text":"Right? Both of those started out\nas small, socially conscious companies"},{"time":394840,"text":"that ended up becoming\nso popular with consumers"},{"time":398000,"text":"that the giants Unilever\nand Clorox bought them"},{"time":401080,"text":"for hundreds of millions of dollars"},{"time":403880,"text":"each."},{"time":405840,"text":"But here's the important thing."},{"time":407400,"text":"Those corporations realized"},{"time":408760,"text":"that if they wanted to protect\nthe value of their investments,"},{"time":411720,"text":"they had to preserve\nthat socially conscious mission."},{"time":414240,"text":"If they didn't keep adding in\nthose extra words"},{"time":416480,"text":"of environmentally friendly\nand socially conscious,"},{"time":418920,"text":"those brands wouldn't make more money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422440,"text":"But maybe this is just the exception\nthe proves the rule, right?"},{"time":425800,"text":"The serious companies\nthat fund our economy"},{"time":428360,"text":"and that fund our retirements\nand that really make the world go round,"},{"time":431680,"text":"they need to stick to making more money."},{"time":434960,"text":"So, Harvard Business School\nactually researched this,"},{"time":437680,"text":"and they found something fascinating."},{"time":439466,"text":"If you had invested a dollar 20 years ago"},{"time":442120,"text":"in a portfolio of companies"},{"time":443800,"text":"that focused narrowly on making more money"},{"time":446040,"text":"quarter by quarter,"},{"time":448000,"text":"that one dollar"},{"time":449440,"text":"would have grown\nto 14 dollars and 46 cents."},{"time":453320,"text":"That's not bad until you consider"},{"time":455600,"text":"that if instead\nyou'd invested that same dollar"},{"time":458640,"text":"in a portfolio of companies"},{"time":460320,"text":"that focused on growing their business"},{"time":462154,"text":"and on the most important\nenvironmental and social issues,"},{"time":466040,"text":"that one dollar would have grown"},{"time":468240,"text":"to 28 dollars and 36 cents."},{"time":472240,"text":"almost twice as much sweet porridge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475160,"text":"Now, let's be clear, they didn't make\nthat outperformance"},{"time":478160,"text":"by giving away money\nto seem like a nice corporate citizen."},{"time":481080,"text":"They did it by focusing on the things\nthat matter to their business,"},{"time":484320,"text":"like wasting less energy and water"},{"time":486760,"text":"in their manufacturing processes;"},{"time":488560,"text":"like making sure the CEO contracts\nhad the CEOs incentivized"},{"time":491960,"text":"for the long-term results of the company\nand the communities they served,"},{"time":495440,"text":"not just quarterly results;"},{"time":496840,"text":"or building a first class culture"},{"time":499160,"text":"that would have higher employee loyalty,"},{"time":501520,"text":"retention and productivity."},{"time":504480,"text":"Now, Harvard's not alone."},{"time":505760,"text":"Oxford also did a research study\nwhere they examined 120 different studies"},{"time":509800,"text":"looking at the effect\nof sustainability and economic results,"},{"time":513280,"text":"and they found\ntime and time and time again"},{"time":516080,"text":"that the companies that cared\nabout these kinds of important things"},{"time":519960,"text":"actually had better\noperational efficiency,"},{"time":522600,"text":"lower cost of capital"},{"time":524440,"text":"and better performance\nin their stock price."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527320,"text":"And then there's Al Gore."},{"time":528880,"text":"So 20 years ago, when I worked\nfor Al Gore in the White House,"},{"time":531840,"text":"he was one of the early pioneers\npleading with businesses and governments"},{"time":535320,"text":"to pay attention to the challenges\nof climate change."},{"time":538040,"text":"Post-White House, he opened\nan investment firm called Generation,"},{"time":541112,"text":"where he baked environmental\nsustainability and other things"},{"time":544400,"text":"right into the core investment process."},{"time":546840,"text":"And at the time there was\na good bit of skepticism about his views."},{"time":550520,"text":"Ten years later, his track record\nis one more proof point"},{"time":554280,"text":"that sustainable investing done right\ncan be sound investing."},{"time":558000,"text":"Far from making less sweet porridge"},{"time":559880,"text":"because he added\nsustainability into the mix,"},{"time":562280,"text":"he actually significantly\noutperformed the benchmark."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565560,"text":"Now, sustainable investing,"},{"time":567120,"text":"the good news is\nit doesn't require a magic spell"},{"time":570920,"text":"and it doesn't require\nsome investment secret,"},{"time":574120,"text":"and it's not just for the elite."},{"time":575720,"text":"It is not just about private equity\nfor billionaires."},{"time":579240,"text":"It's not just groovy-sounding investments\nlike clean technology"},{"time":582217,"text":"or microfinance in emerging markets"},{"time":583937,"text":"or artisanal bakeries in Brooklyn."},{"time":587000,"text":"It's about stocks and bonds\nand Fortune 500 companies."},{"time":590040,"text":"It's about mutual funds."},{"time":591280,"text":"It's about all the things"},{"time":592760,"text":"we already see in the market today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":595520,"text":"So here's why I'm convinced"},{"time":597520,"text":"that we collectively have the power"},{"time":599680,"text":"to make sustainable investing\nthe new normal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603560,"text":"First, the proof points\nare coming out all the time"},{"time":607800,"text":"that sustainable investing done right,"},{"time":609840,"text":"preserving all the same\ngood principles of investing,"},{"time":613080,"text":"the traditional sphere, can pay."},{"time":615520,"text":"It makes sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617360,"text":"Secondly,"},{"time":618800,"text":"the biggest obstacle standing in our way"},{"time":620960,"text":"may actually just be in our heads."},{"time":623520,"text":"We just need to let go of that myth"},{"time":625600,"text":"that if you add your values\ninto your investment thinking,"},{"time":629880,"text":"that you get less sweet porridge."},{"time":631520,"text":"And once you get rid of the fable,"},{"time":633200,"text":"you can actually start appreciating\nthose facts we've been talking about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636680,"text":"And third, the future is already here."},{"time":638680,"text":"Sustainable investment today\nis a 20 trillion dollar market"},{"time":641680,"text":"and it's the fastest-growing segment\nof the investment industry."},{"time":645080,"text":"In the United States,\nit has grown enormously, as you can see."},{"time":648320,"text":"It now represents\none out of every six dollars"},{"time":651040,"text":"under professional management\nin the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654400,"text":"So what are we waiting for?"},{"time":657160,"text":"For me, it goes back to the inspiration\nthat I received from my mother."},{"time":661240,"text":"She knew that she wanted a life"},{"time":662800,"text":"where she would have the freedom\nto make her own choices"},{"time":666280,"text":"and to have her voice heard\nand write her own story."},{"time":669520,"text":"She was passionate about that goal"},{"time":672000,"text":"and she was clear that she would let\nno army, no obstacle,"},{"time":675640,"text":"no big institution stand in her way."},{"time":679040,"text":"She made it to the States,"},{"time":680920,"text":"and she became a teacher,"},{"time":682680,"text":"an award-winning author"},{"time":684400,"text":"and a mother,"},{"time":685680,"text":"and ended up sending\nher daughters to Harvard."},{"time":688400,"text":"And these days, you can tell\nthat she is amply comfortable"},{"time":691520,"text":"holding court in the most powerful\ninstitutions in the world."},{"time":695600,"text":"It seems almost too prophetic"},{"time":697520,"text":"that her name in Korean means"},{"time":699840,"text":"\"passionate clarity.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":702280,"text":"Passionate clarity:"},{"time":703960,"text":"that's what I think we need\nto drive change."},{"time":706760,"text":"Passion about the change\nwe want to see in the world,"},{"time":710120,"text":"and clarity that we are able\nto help chart the course."},{"time":714520,"text":"We have more opportunity today\nthan ever before"},{"time":717520,"text":"to make choices."},{"time":719160,"text":"We have more power than ever before\nto make our voices heard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":724800,"text":"So change your perspective."},{"time":728240,"text":"Vote with your small change."},{"time":729960,"text":"Invest in the change\nyou want to see in the world."},{"time":733800,"text":"Change the fables"},{"time":735600,"text":"and change the markets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":737280,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":738520,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}